title: Esma Redzepova - collection (macedonian gypsy-queen)
description:
This is actually a repost of a long since dead torrent.
I have no information as to the names of the albums. My guess is that both are compilations. Some of the tracks sound like synths and beatboxes (which i'm not particularly fond of), while others have the good old macedonian acoustic sound.
(I'll be uploading some good macedonian gypsy-stuff when i get to ripping the vinyls. The entire 'tanec' series is waiting on my shelves)
